      {
        "title": "Blaster",
        "excerpt": "Blasters are combat mages who excel in causing massive magical destruction. They blast creatures and structures to pieces with long-range advanced combat magic and elemental explosions. Blasters are often employed as soldiers or warmages, as their explosive area spells can devastate entire formations of mundane soldiers.   Blaster talents focus entirely on causing damage. Most of these talents are different kinds of magical blast attacks, and the rest buff other magical attacks. Blaster talents include almost no defensive or utility abilities, which can make blasters into glass cannons. Blaster ribbons give them minor utility abilities to support their offense.   Examples of blasters in fiction include the black mages from Final Fantasy, any D&amp;D caster that specializes in evocation, and most combat-oriented mages and sorcerers from RPGs.     Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Burning Arrow                  Novice                                                              You conjure a fiery arrow that continues burning after it hits                                               Dangerous Sorcery                  Novice                                                              You boost the magical energy you channeled into a recent spell                                               Elemental Adept                  Novice                                      You can bypass your enemies’ resistances to particular damage types                                               Icy Rebuke                  Novice                                                              You retaliate against an attack with a pulse of cold energy                                               Lightning Beam                  Novice                                                              You begin to emanate a beam of lightning that continuously zaps enemies                                               Power Bolt                  Novice                                                              You fire a bolt of damaging magical energies that impacts with violent force                                               Close Combat Mage                  Veteran                                      You can cast ranged spells very effectively in close quarters                                               Fireball                  Veteran                                                              You conjure a mote of fire that explodes into a vast fireball                                               Awesome Destruction                  Ribbon                                      Your destructive magic awes and scares everyone who can see it                                               Minor Blast                  Ribbon                                                              You scatter a small amount of power to deal a tiny bit of damage to several targets                                               Shatter                  Ribbon                                                              You send out powerful sonic waves that shatter an object                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Talents                                                                                                                                                  Burning Arrow                                   Novice                                Attack              Fire              Spell                                Cost         2 Mana              Range         120 feet              Duration         Sustained, up to 1 minute                  Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Agility DC.      Critical Success   Double damage   Success   Your target takes 2d10 damage   Heightened   For each +2 Mana, this spell’s damage increases by 1d10.                                           Dangerous Sorcery                                   Novice                                  Trigger         You deal damage with a spell you cast this turn                  The triggering damage increases by 1d6 (against all of the spell’s targets).                                           Elemental Adept                         Novice                 Choose one of the following traits: Acid, Cold, Electricity, Fire, or Sonic. Spells you cast with that trait ignore all Shields.                                           Icy Rebuke                                   Novice                                Attack              Cold              Spell                                Trigger         You take damage from an attack              Cost         1 Mana              Target         The creature that made the triggering attack                  Make a Magic attack roll against the target’s Agility DC.      Success   Your target takes 3d10 damage   Failure   Half damage   Heightened   For each +2 Mana, the damage increases by 3d10.                                           Lightning Beam                                   Novice                    Zap                                                     Attack              Electricity                                Range         30 feet                  Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Defense.      Success   Your target takes 2d10 damage   Failure   Half damage                                 Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Duration         1 minute, or until you use Zap three times                  You can use the Zap power.   Heightened   For each +1 Mana, the damage of Zap increases by 1d10.                                           Power Bolt                                   Novice                                Attack              Cantrip              Force              Spell                                Cost         0 Mana              Range         60 feet                  Make a Magic attack roll against the target’s Defense.      Critical Success   Double damage   Success   Your target takes 2d6 damage   Heightened   For each +1 Mana, the damage increases by 2d6.                                           Close Combat Mage                         Veteran                 When you use an Attack spell with a range of at least 30 feet, you can decrease the range to Touch to get a +2 bonus to the attack roll.                                           Fireball                                   Veteran                                Attack              Fire              Spell                                Cost         3 Mana              Range         500 feet              Area         20-foot burst                  Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Agility DC.      Success   Your target takes 4d6 damage   Failure   Half damage   Heightened   For each +1 Mana, the damage increases by 1d6.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Ribbons                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Awesome Destruction                         Ribbon                 You have advantage on Spirit+Provoke rolls to intimidate people who have seen you cast a Blaster spell in the past minute.                                           Minor Blast                                   Ribbon                                Cantrip              Spell                                Cost         0 Mana              Range         120 feet              Target         Up to ten targets you can see within range                  Choose one of the Cold, Electricity, or Fire traits. This spell gains that trait. Your target takes 1 damage.                                           Shatter                                   Ribbon                                Cantrip              Sonic              Spell                                Cost         0 Mana              Range         30 feet                  If your target is an inanimate, unattended object, it takes 1d6 damage.   Heightened   For a total of 1 Mana, this spell gains an area of a 10-foot burst. For each additional +1 Mana, the burst’s radius increases by 10 feet.",
        "url": "/blaster.html"
      }
      
