      {
        "title": "Druid",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Befriend Animal                  Novice                                                              You befriend an animal, making it your trusted companion                                               Entangle                  Novice                                                              You conjure ensnaring vines from the ground to trap your foes                                               Goodberry                  Novice                                                              You conjure a handful of berries with magical healing properties                                               Magic Acorns                  Novice                                                              You imbue several small projectiles with the fury of nature                                               Thorn Whip                  Novice                                                              You strike at an enemy with writhing thorn-covered vines                                               Awaken                  Veteran                                                              You grant an animal humanoid intelligence and opposable thumbs                                               Instant Tree                  Novice                                                              You cause a tree to appear, growing with explosive force                                               Detect Poison                  Ribbon                                                              You identify and locate any nearby poisons or diseases                                               Friend of Nature                  Ribbon                                      Animals are naturally friendly towards you                                               Land's Stride                  Ribbon                                      You ignore simple natural hazards that impede movement                                               Spark of Growth                  Ribbon                                                              You encourage a plant to grow magically quickly                                               Speak with Animals                  Ribbon                                      You can communicate simple concepts with animals                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Talents                                                                                                                                                                                              Befriend Animal                                   Novice                                Attack              Auditory              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Target         A Beast creature you can reach that has CR no higher than your character level              Duration         24 hours, until you decide to end it, or until you or one of your companions harms the target                  Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Spirit DC. If your target is already friendly towards you, this attack automatically succeeds.      Success   Your target becomes totally loyal to you and gains the Minion trait. Your target obeys any command you give it, even putting itself at risk, unless those directions are obviously suicidal.                                           Entangle                                   Novice                                Attack              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Range         60 feet              Area         20-foot burst              Requirements         Your target is on the ground              Duration         Forever                  Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Agility DC      Critical Success   Your target is restrained   Success   Your target is immobilized   Failure   Your target is slowed until the end of its next turn                                           Goodberry                                   Novice                                Healing              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Duration         1 hour                  Up to 10 berries appear in your hand. A creature can eat a berry (or feed it to an ally) with the Interact power. Eating a berry heals 1 health and provides enough nourishment to sustain a normal human for one day. Any uneaten berries disappear when the duration ends.                                           Magic Acorns                                   Novice                                Cantrip              Spell                                Cost         0 Mana              Target         Up to 5 acorns, nuts, pinecones, seeds, or similar objects you can reach              Duration         1 minute                  The targets are magically enhanced to act as amazing projectiles. These projectiles count as ranged weapons with a base damage of 1d8 Bludgeoning and a range of 60 feet.   Heightened   If you add +1 Mana, all the projectiles gain one of the following effects.   Fiery. The projectiles explode with a burst of flame when they hit. On a successful Strike, all creatures in a 5-foot burst around the target take 1d6 Fire damage.   Slowing. The projectiles cover their target in sticky sap. On a successful Strike, the target is slowed until the end of its next turn.                                           Thorn Whip                                   Novice                                Attack              Cantrip              Piercing              Spell                                Cost         0 Mana              Range         30 feet                  Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Agility DC.      Critical Success   Double damage   Success   Your target takes 2d6 damage and is pulled up to 10 feet towards you   Heightened   For each +1 Mana, the damage increases by 1d6.                                           Awaken                                   Veteran                                Ritual              Spell                                Cost         5 Mana              Target         One Beast creature you can reach                  Your target becomes sentient, gaining intelligence as an Awakened. Your target’s form morphs to become more humanoid: they gain the proper limbs, can breathe air, gain opposable thumbs, can speak humanoid language, and so on.   After the transformation, your target is usually friendly towards you, though they may be shocked by the sudden change. If your target was loyal to you before the transformation, they act as a Minion loyal to you for the next hour, after which they become a normal NPC.                                           Instant Tree                                   Novice                                Attack              Bludgeoning              Spell                                Cost         3 Mana              Range         60 feet              Area         20-foot line                  A tree grows almost instantly, starting from the specified point, to fill the spell’s area. You choose the species of tree. Once the tree is done growing, it stays around forever as a normal tree.   Make a Magic attack roll against your target’s Agility DC.      Critical Success   Double damage and double push distance   Success   Your target takes 4d10 damage and is pushed 20 feet away from the base of the tree   Failure   Half damage   Heightened   For each +1 Mana, the damage increases by 1d10, the area extends by 10 feet, and the push distance increases by 10 feet.         We can never forget the Treeagle incident of 2015.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Ribbons                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Detect Poison                                   Ribbon                                Ritual              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Area         30-foot burst                  You detect all poisons, poisonous creatures, diseases, and diseased creatures in the area. You sense the precise location and the exact type of poison or disease.                                           Friend of Nature                         Ribbon                 Animals and intelligent plants tend to like you. Unless given reason to act otherwise, they will treat you as a trusted friend or ally. If you have the Speak with Animals power, you can usually get animals to perform simple favors for you.                                           Land's Stride                         Ribbon                 Moving through nonmagical difficult terrain costs you no extra movement. You can also pass through nonmagical plants without being slowed by them and without taking damage from them if they have thorns, spines, or a similar hazard.                                           Spark of Growth                                   Ribbon                                Cantrip              Healing              Ritual              Spell                                Cost         0 Mana              Target         A nonmagical plant you can reach              Requirements         Your target hasn’t been affected by Spark of Growth in the past week                  Your target instantly undergoes up to a year of normal growth. The plant might grow in size, gain or shed leaves, or grow blossoms.   Heightened   For each +1 Mana, your target heals 1d6 health or recovers from one disease afflicting it.                                           Speak with Animals                         Ribbon                                Auditory               You can let animals can understand your speech, no matter what language you speak in. In turn, you can decipher an animal’s intent by interpreting its noises and motions. Most animals lack the intelligence to understand sophisticated concepts.",
        "url": "/druid.html"
      }
      
